		</form></span></div></div><div class="topper-basic__sponsor"><span class="topper-basic__sponsor-text">Supported by HSBC Global Private Banking</span></div></div><div class="topper-basic__border_bottom"></div></div><div class="info-box" style="background-color:#faeadc"><div class="info-box__content"><div class="info-box__body"><p>Keeping informed of geopolitical and economic developments has never been more important for preserving or passing on wealth. This hub from FT Group titles Financial Times, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.pwmnet.com/ft-wealth-management">Professional Wealth Management</a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.ftadviser.com/FT-Wealth-Management ">FT Adviser</a>, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.ftadviser.com/asset-allocator/">Asset Allocator</a> and <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://asia.nikkei.com/Business/Markets/Wealth-Management">Nikkei Asia</a>, and supported by HSBC Global Private Banking, will bring all the essential wealth management news and in-depth analysis from around the world.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div><div class="container container--w-div flow-row"><div class="container__item flow-ln-1"><div class="o-teaser o-teaser--top-story o-teaser--landscape o-teaser--has-image js-teaser" data-id="b6771b3a-2d28-4891-b6bd-bc75dff245d8"><div class="o-teaser__content"><div class="o-teaser__meta"><a class="o-teaser__tag" data-trackable="teaser-tag" href="/stream/4d6444b6-0dda-474b-89be-2cfc07eeae7d" aria-label="Category: Professional Wealth Management">Professional Wealth Management</a></div><div class="o-teaser__heading"><a href="https://www.pwmnet.com/the-evolution-of-wealth-management-in-the-middle-east" data-trackable="heading-link" class="js-teaser-heading-link">The evolution of wealth management in the Middle East</a></div><p class="o-teaser__standfirst"><a href="https://www.pwmnet.com/the-evolution-of-wealth-management-in-the-middle-east" data-trackable="standfirst-link" tabindex="-1" class="js-teaser-standfirst-link">Dubai has been the leadering financial hub in the region since its International Financial Centre took off in 2004</a></p></div><div class="o-teaser__image-container js-teaser-image-container"><a href="https://www.pwmnet.com/the-evolution-of-wealth-management-in-the-middle-east" data-trackable="image-link" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true"><div class="o-teaser__image-placeholder"><img class="o-teaser__image" src="https://www.ft.com/__origami/service/image/v2/images/raw/https%3A%2F%2Fd1e00ek4ebabms.cloudfront.net%2Fproduction%2Fde7f9277-bdf8-4fc4-bed5-49059c9bfc4a.jpg?source=next&amp;fit=scale-down&amp;dpr=2&amp;width=640" alt=""/></div></a></div></div></div><div class="container__item flow-ln-2 LX:flow-ln-4"><div class="o-teaser o-teaser--small o-teaser--stacked o-teaser--has-image js-teaser" data-id="51aa8e96-610d-431d-8a88-53b42e83a89b"><div class="o-teaser__content"><div class="o-teaser__meta"><a class="o-teaser__tag" data-trackable="teaser-tag" href="/ft-wealth-management" aria-label="Category: FT Wealth Management">FT Wealth Management</a></div><div class="o-teaser__heading"><a href="/content/51aa8e96-610d-431d-8a88-53b42e83a89b" data-trackable="heading-link" class="js-teaser-heading-link">Investors Trump-proof portfolios as risks rise ahead of US election</a></div></div><div class="o-teaser__image-container js-teaser-image-container"><a href="/content/51aa8e96-610d-431d-8a88-53b42e83a89b" data-trackable="image-link" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true"><div class="o-teaser__image-placeholder"><img class="o-teaser__image" src="https://www.ft.com/__origami/service/image/v2/images/raw/https%3A%2F%2Fd1e00ek4ebabms.cloudfront.net%2Fproduction%2F30c5fe91-5eba-479b-a8cc-7793cdddd40b.jpg?source=next&amp;fit=scale-down&amp;dpr=2&amp;width=340" alt=""/></div></a></div></div></div><div class="container__item flow-ln-2 LX:flow-ln-4"><div class="